      <preamble>
         <formula name="enactingText">
            <p>The Scottish Ministers make the following Regulations in exercise of the powers conferred by section 9(2) and (3) of the Damages (Investment Returns and Periodical Payments) (Scotland) Act 2019<noteRef href="#f00001" class="footnote" marker="1"/>.</p>
         </formula>
