      <body>
         <hcontainer name="regulation" eId="regulation-1">
            <heading>Citation and commencement</heading>
            <num>1.</num>
            <content>
               <p>These Regulations may be cited as the Damages (Investment Returns and Periodical Payments) (Scotland) Act 2019 (Commencement No. 1) Regulations 2019 and come into force on 1 July 2019.</p>
            </content>
         </hcontainer>
         <hcontainer name="regulation" eId="regulation-2">
            <heading>Appointed day</heading>
            <num>2.</num>
            <content>
               <p>The day appointed for the coming into force of sections 1 and 2 (returns on investment of damages) and the schedule (investments: setting rate of return) of the Damages (Investment Returns and Periodical Payments) (Scotland) Act 2019 is 1 July 2019.</p>
            </content>
         </hcontainer>
         <hcontainer name="regulation" eId="regulation-3">
            <heading>Amendment of the Damages Act 1996</heading>
            <num>3.</num>
            <paragraph eId="regulation-3-1">
               <num>(1)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>In the provisions of schedule B1 of the Damages Act 1996<noteRef href="#f00002" class="footnote" marker="2"/> mentioned in paragraph (2), for the words from “the day” to the end of the provision substitute “1 July 2019”.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="regulation-3-2">
               <num>(2)</num>
               <intro>
                  <p>Those provisions are—</p>
               </intro>
               <subparagraph eId="regulation-3-2-a">
                  <num>(a)</num>
                  <content>
                     <p>paragraph 1(3)(b),</p>
                  </content>
               </subparagraph>
               <subparagraph eId="regulation-3-2-b">
                  <num>(b)</num>
                  <content>
                     <p>paragraph 27(3),</p>
                  </content>
               </subparagraph>
               <subparagraph eId="regulation-3-2-c">
                  <num>(c)</num>
                  <content>
                     <p>paragraph 29(2), and</p>
                  </content>
               </subparagraph>
               <subparagraph eId="regulation-3-2-d">
                  <num>(d)</num>
                  <content>
                     <p>paragraph 30(2).</p>
                  </content>
               </subparagraph>
            </paragraph>
